'''Dave''' is a flight attendant who was uninjured during the turbulence.

==History==
Dave was attending a flight out of Seattle when they hit severe turbulence, injuring several passengers and his fellow flight attendant [[Candace]]. Dave helped access supplies and when [[Lance]] went into cardiac arrest, Dave assisted Nathan in treating him. They then got approval for an emergency landing in Sioux Falls, where the plane was met with ambulances.

==Career==
He is a flight attendant.
